title: #92Noon! 9am Hour 10/5 - Talkers/Cronin
description: Frivolity kicks off #92Noon on a Tuesday, followed by ESPN.com's Courtney Cronin making her studio appearance for most of the first hour. Paul Guenther's Vikings report tucked into the mix as well on a Crucial Catch Day at the Fan!
